Government economic policy and market regulations have an influence on the competitiveness and profitability of businesses. 
To ensure that SMEs thrive, NNEW has put together a workshop where CBN will enlighten the participants on VAIDS and other tax-related issues. 
There will also be a review of the budget before the National Assembly and discuss how SMEs can take its advantages to better their businesses in 2018.
